  test:full: Ō£ō Present

=== Expected Mock Chain Structure ===
After fixes, Supabase mocks should support:
  - from().select().eq().single() ŌåÆ { data, error }
  - from().insert().select().single() ŌåÆ { data, error }
  - from().select().eq().gt().single() ŌåÆ { data, error }
  - from().update().eq().single() ŌåÆ { data, error }
